*Write operations — <<<govern: [ transaction ]>>>

  The <<<CreateArticleService>>> declares <<<ArticleRepository>>> as a plain parameter.  The YAML
  file wraps the step in a read/write transaction via <<<govern: [ transaction ]>>>.  If the
  service method throws an exception the transaction is automatically rolled back:

