*Testing

  Tests use standard Spring Boot <<<MockMvc>>>.  The <<<ArticleRepository>>> is injected for
  setup and teardown — OfficeFloor tests do not require any special utilities.

  <<<deleteArticleNotFound>>> verifies that the <<<notFound>>> exception-handler step
  (which also carries <<<govern: [ transaction ]>>>) returns a proper 404 within the same
  transaction.  <<<replaceAllArticles>>> verifies that the two-step <<<replace-all>>> endpoint
  atomically replaces all existing articles with a single new one:

